{"tid":1655151,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"遭割頸警長留醫ICU","createTime":"2019-10-15T02:29:02.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-15T05:33:02.000Z","uid":82010,"like":0,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"bb33119d47a7546f23d70106e563a09b673cf507","tid":1655151,"uid":82010,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T02:29:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/T8CMqLU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FT8CMqLU.jpg&h=50a91ce3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/EZJ7UEi.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEZJ7UEi.png&h=0175c5d7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n一名警員13日在觀塘執勤期間被一名黑衣人以利刃割傷頸部，目前仍在深切治療部(ICU)留醫，已脫離危險，目前情況穩定。警方昨日拘捕兩人，涉嫌割頸的19歲中六學生仍在將軍澳警署扣留。<br />\n據了解，遇襲警長43歲，隸屬東九龍警區衝鋒隊，人稱「祥哥」，右頸有約3至4厘米鎅傷，幸未傷及大動脈。<br />\n事發於昨午約5時半，消息稱，警方接報指已關閉的觀塘站，有一批黑衣人不斷搖晃近apm商場出入口的港鐵大閘，一批防暴警到場了解，發現破壞者已四散，防暴警收隊離去之際，一名在人群中的戴眼鏡黑衣男，突持鎅刀從後割向一名警長右頸，該名警長當時即血流如注。<br />\n另據悉，被捕的19歲男中六學生就讀位於上水金錢村的新界喇沙中學。"},{"pid":"30b7d0f8f2bf5d6f9b0730ade77aec86d1be3429","tid":1655151,"uid":14897,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T05:21:22.000Z","msg":"咁都要入icu<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"84a0f1818a9f2ca4c41c0ccbf854fcea74b671fb","tid":1655151,"uid":266741,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"bb33119d47a7546f23d70106e563a09b673cf507","tid":1655151,"uid":82010,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T02:29:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/T8CMqLU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FT8CMqLU.jpg&h=50a91ce3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/EZJ7UEi.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEZJ7UEi.png&h=0175c5d7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n一名警員13日在觀塘執勤期間被一名黑衣人以利刃割傷頸部，目前